data.description: Newer ranch style home located in Shawnee School District. This home is beautifully maintained with laminate floors throughout for easy cleaning.  The foyer welcomes visitors with guest closet and 2 guest bedrooms area to the left of foyer with private guest bath.  Located in the rear of this home is the  Master bedroom has private bath with walk-in shower and huge walk-in closet.  The entry hall opens into wonderful great room with living room (19x13), kitchen with island and seating for two.  This area also has a dining area for table seating (Total area 19x12).  The crisp white cabinets in the kitchen are very attractive has plenty of storage plus nice pantry.  Kitchen is equipped with stainless applicances to include range, refrigerator, dishwasher and over range microwave.  There is a 10 x 12 deck in the rear off the dining area.  The yard has a privacy fence.  All faux wood blinds stay with home.  The basement is unfinished and has an egress window for emergency exit, ready for finishing by the new owner.  Gas avg, $83, Electric avg. $65, Water avg. $37, trash $81/qtr.  This home has an FHA assumable loan with a 3.5% interest rate.  Call for details.
